"    #####    {        translations:            [                {                    english_version: \"Six people are missing after a bridge collapsed in Baltimore Harbour. The accident may affect coal shipments for weeks.\",                    english_title: \"Bridge collapse in Baltimore Harbour\",                    translated_version: \"Seis personas est\u00e1n desaparecidas despu\u00e9s de que un puente se derrumb\u00f3 en el Puerto de Baltimore. El accidente podr\u00eda afectar los env\u00edos de carb\u00f3n durante semanas.\",                    translated_title: \"Colapso del puente en el Puerto de Baltimore\"                },                {                    english_version: \"Visa and Mastercard will reduce payment-processing fees for merchants in America. This could save merchants $30bn over five years.\",                    english_title: \"Reduction in payment-processing fees\",                    translated_version: \"Visa y Mastercard reducir\u00e1n las tarifas de procesamiento de pagos para los comerciantes en Am\u00e9rica. Esto podr\u00eda ahorrarles a los comerciantes $30 mil millones en cinco a\u00f1os.\",                    translated_title: \"Reducci\u00f3n en las tarifas de procesamiento de pagos\"                },                {                    english_version: \"America's Supreme Court is considering a case on mifepristone, a drug used in abortions. The court seems sceptical of arguments to impose greater restrictions on the drug.\",                    english_title: \"Supreme Court case on mifepristone\",                    translated_version: \"La Corte Suprema de Am\u00e9rica est\u00e1 considerando un caso sobre mifepristona, un medicamento utilizado en abortos. La corte parece esc\u00e9ptica sobre los argumentos para imponer mayores restricciones al medicamento.\",                    translated_title: \"Caso de la Corte Suprema sobre la mifepristona\"                },                {                    english_version: \"Julian Assange may not be immediately extradited to America. He can appeal against his extradition if certain conditions are not met.\",                    english_title: \"Extradition case of Julian Assange\",                    translated_version: \"Julian Assange puede que no sea extraditado inmediatamente a Am\u00e9rica. \u00c9l puede apelar contra su extradici\u00f3n si no se cumplen ciertas condiciones.\",                    translated_title: \"Caso de extradici\u00f3n de Julian Assange\"                },                {                    english_version: \"Israel's cabinet is discussing legislation to exempt religious students from military service. The number of exempt students has increased significantly.\",                    english_title: \"Exemption of religious students from military service in Israel\",                    translated_version: \"El gabinete de Israel est\u00e1 discutiendo una ley para eximir a los estudiantes religiosos del servicio militar. El n\u00famero de estudiantes exentos ha aumentado significativamente.\",                    translated_title: \"Exenci\u00f3n de estudiantes religiosos del servicio militar en Israel\"                }            ]    }    #####"